Question: Sixfab GmbH CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Sixfab GmbH

Sixfab Jumpstart 5G

- IoT computer integrated with Quectel RM502Q-AE 5G NR Sub-6GHz modem
- Patent-pending Sixfab designed internal antenna for excellent performance
- Specialized plastic enclosure with a thermal system for optimal performance
- Suitable for industries and sectors requiring high-speed and reliable IoT connectivity
- Accessible platform for exploring and harnessing 5G technology in IoT applications
- Applicable in various use cases and scenarios

Products:
- Sixfab 5G Modem Kit for Raspberry Pi 5
- Sixfab 4G/LTE Cellular Modem Kit for Raspberry Pi
- Sixfab Jumpstart 5G
- Sixfab Pico LTE
- Sixfab CORE
- Raspberry Pi 3G/4G&LTE Base HAT
- Raspberry Pi 5G Development Kit
- NVIDIA Jetson Nano 4G/LTE Cellular Modem Kit
- Raspberry Pi Cellular IoT Kit (LTE-M)
- Sixfab Power Management & UPS HAT
